<h1> Syntax </h1>
<br>
practice         : sees what you can learn where you are<br>
practice [skill] : practices specified skill<br>
<br>
<h1> Description </h1>
<br>
Practice is the command used to pay a trainer to improve you in a skill. <br>
Practicing costs gold and experience points.  In most towns there are<br>
trainers who can teach you the basic skills, but it may not be obvious<br>
who they are.  An example is Prenslie in Chiiron can train some spells. <br>
Skills and spells above level 15 generally must be sought after outside<br>
of towns.<br>
<br>
**See 'help practices'(with the 's' for info on the change).**<br>
